WEBVTT

00:00.174 --> 00:05.122
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:06.094 --> 00:08.802
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.934 --> 00:13.942
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.966 --> 00:18.722
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.758 --> 00:22.786
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.790 --> 00:27.734
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.758 --> 00:31.030
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:31.054 --> 00:34.518
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.542 --> 00:39.790
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.790 --> 00:41.408
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.408 --> 00:44.886
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.910 --> 00:48.182
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.206 --> 00:53.878
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.902 --> 00:55.246
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.246 --> 00:58.582
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.606 --> 01:01.954
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:02.062 --> 01:07.259
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.259 --> 01:08.942
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.942 --> 01:12.342
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.366 --> 01:15.766
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.790 --> 01:21.366
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.390 --> 01:24.802
♪ I love you ♪

01:27.080 --> 01:27.870
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.870 --> 01:31.212
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 1=

01:31.469 --> 01:33.778
(- Shengshengman.
- I'm here.)

01:41.922 --> 01:44.137
Hurry up. We'll be late for breakfast.

01:44.161 --> 01:45.181
Brother.

01:51.521 --> 01:52.978
Sheng, I'm here.

01:53.002 --> 01:54.377
Can't we talk on the phone?

01:54.401 --> 01:56.461
Why the voice chat room?

01:56.562 --> 01:57.841
I'm boosting my EXP.

01:57.841 --> 01:59.461
Fine.

01:59.642 --> 02:01.898
You'll be
the music director for the event.

02:01.922 --> 02:03.862
Do a good job.

02:04.121 --> 02:06.618
- Okay.
- Without a payment, though.

02:06.642 --> 02:08.018
What are you eating?

02:08.042 --> 02:09.382
I tell you.

02:11.121 --> 02:13.582
I'm having this amazing bun.

02:13.721 --> 02:15.982
I'll get you one next time.

02:18.901 --> 02:20.302
(Ancheng Bus)
The bus is here.

02:22.162 --> 02:23.018
On the bus now.

02:23.042 --> 02:24.941
I'll call you from the dorm.

02:25.521 --> 02:27.578
Don't hang up. Let's keep talking.

02:27.602 --> 02:29.858
How was the birthday dinner
with your cousin?

02:29.882 --> 02:31.578
Did you use the coupons?

02:31.602 --> 02:32.941
Yeah.

02:33.922 --> 02:37.537
The pork stomach with chicken
was super good.

02:37.561 --> 02:38.458
(Geng Xiaoxing)
Sheng.

02:38.482 --> 02:41.657
Are you tormenting yourself or me?

02:41.681 --> 02:42.738
I tell you.

02:42.762 --> 02:44.497
It's the first time I realized

02:44.521 --> 02:47.898
how amazing it is to stew them together.

02:47.922 --> 02:48.817
Think about it.

02:48.841 --> 02:51.377
The soup turns white

02:51.401 --> 02:56.058
and gives off the aroma
of herbs and pepper.

02:56.082 --> 02:57.058
Geng Xiaoxing.

02:57.082 --> 02:59.298
I'll take you to try it once.

02:59.322 --> 03:00.178
I swear.

03:00.202 --> 03:01.618
The one next to

03:01.642 --> 03:04.702
the First People's Hospital
is one of the best.

03:06.241 --> 03:08.262
Why are you silent?

03:10.362 --> 03:12.458
It's a famous Cantonese Hakka dish.

03:12.482 --> 03:16.417
You can try to make it at home.

03:16.441 --> 03:18.181
(Qiang Qingci)

03:18.401 --> 03:20.021
(It's Qiang Qingci!)

03:20.322 --> 03:22.298
(Why is he in my voice chat room?)

03:22.322 --> 03:25.061
It just takes time.

03:25.441 --> 03:28.181
And it's troublesome
to wash the pork stomach.

03:28.281 --> 03:30.382
It's good for health.

03:36.121 --> 03:37.941
I remember there are

03:38.561 --> 03:39.662
dates,

03:39.882 --> 03:41.302
Dang Shen,

03:42.042 --> 03:43.338
Polygonatum Root,

03:43.362 --> 03:44.781
goji berries,

03:46.521 --> 03:49.662
and some other common spices.

03:52.721 --> 03:55.501
Seal the chicken
in the pork stomach with toothpicks.

03:56.441 --> 03:57.982
Stew them well.

03:58.721 --> 04:00.977
(Qiang Qingci)
Mr. Qiang Qingci.

04:01.001 --> 04:03.501
Can you hear me?

04:08.482 --> 04:09.621
Sheng.

04:10.081 --> 04:10.898
Sheng.

04:10.922 --> 04:12.701
(Geng Xiaoxing)
I'm back. Still there?

04:15.321 --> 04:17.977
The dorm manager came for an inspection.

04:18.001 --> 04:19.057
Go on.

04:19.081 --> 04:23.381
Pork stomach with chicken.

04:24.001 --> 04:27.458
So you didn't hear Qiang Qingci talking?

04:27.482 --> 04:28.417
Qiang Qingci?

04:28.441 --> 04:29.217
What's that?

04:29.241 --> 04:32.097
The famous dubbing actor Qiang Qingci.

04:32.121 --> 04:33.842
From the Perfect Voice Studio.

04:34.641 --> 04:36.057
I know that studio.

04:36.081 --> 04:37.542
I've heard of it.

04:37.602 --> 04:38.857
How do you spell his name?

04:38.881 --> 04:40.657
Qiang Qingci.

04:40.681 --> 04:43.657
Qiang spells like Q-i-a-n-g.

04:43.681 --> 04:45.498
It means a color.

04:45.522 --> 04:48.338
Ci means "magnetic".

04:48.362 --> 04:49.662
Got it?

04:53.365 --> 04:56.754
(Qiang Qingci entered the room.
Qiang Qingci left the room.)

05:03.962 --> 05:06.701
(Qiang Qingci really
entered my voice chat room, )

05:07.121 --> 05:09.181
(and taught me a recipe.)

05:12.647 --> 05:15.166
(Tianzi No. 1 Recording Studio)
(The Perfect Voice Studio)

05:15.166 --> 05:16.543
(The Perfect Voice Studio)

05:16.543 --> 05:18.450
(Recording, Studio A Control Room)

05:24.149 --> 05:25.042
(Sound Mixing Room)

05:25.042 --> 05:26.422
This is Qiang Qingci.

05:26.722 --> 05:28.102
I'll give it a try.

05:32.962 --> 05:35.061
- Morning, Mr. Juemei.
- Morning.

05:38.081 --> 05:38.922
Morning, Mr. Juemei.

05:38.922 --> 05:40.061
Morning.

05:40.681 --> 05:41.698
Is Qiang Qingci back?

05:41.722 --> 05:42.578
Yeah.

05:42.602 --> 05:44.522
He's sleeping after
the night shift at the hospital.

05:44.522 --> 05:45.922
See you. Let me talk to him.

05:45.922 --> 05:47.222
Be quiet.

05:55.321 --> 05:57.177
Wake up. It's daytime.

05:57.201 --> 06:00.222
Are you coming to the studio's
tenth anniversary ceremony?

06:04.602 --> 06:06.902
Let's wait for the hospital schedule.

06:07.001 --> 06:08.102
Juemei.

06:08.522 --> 06:10.177
I'm craving pork stomach with chicken.

06:10.201 --> 06:11.821
I heard the one next to

06:12.201 --> 06:13.662
my hospital is good.

06:14.001 --> 06:15.778
Okay, I'll book a table.

06:15.802 --> 06:17.061
Hurry up.

06:19.282 --> 06:20.258
Kids.

06:20.282 --> 06:23.057
It will be the final test
after the New Year Festival.

06:23.081 --> 06:26.138
This is your last test
before graduation.

06:26.162 --> 06:28.378
I hope you can enjoy the last semester

06:28.402 --> 06:30.097
no matter whether you're

06:30.121 --> 06:33.698
pursuing further education
or going to work.

06:33.722 --> 06:34.898
Contact me via WeChat

06:34.922 --> 06:36.898
if you have any questions.

06:36.922 --> 06:38.338
That's it for today.

06:38.362 --> 06:39.782
Dismiss.

06:41.241 --> 06:43.542
Goodbye, Madam.

06:44.962 --> 06:46.977
I envy
you secured a place at graduate school.

06:47.001 --> 06:48.138
You don't have to work,

06:48.162 --> 06:50.501
and you can enjoy
more of the school life.

06:50.681 --> 06:52.018
We're from the same dorm.

06:52.042 --> 06:53.818
Why can't I be like you?

06:53.842 --> 06:54.818
Qi Yao.

06:54.842 --> 06:57.222
Haven't you considered
any graduate programs?

06:57.761 --> 06:59.378
I'm dying to work

06:59.402 --> 07:00.857
and support myself.

07:00.881 --> 07:03.061
I can't wait.

07:04.201 --> 07:06.982
You'll see how exhausting it is.

07:08.922 --> 07:10.258
Xiaoxing, are you going

07:10.282 --> 07:11.138
to the company?

07:11.162 --> 07:12.537
No.

07:12.561 --> 07:13.537
I'm just an intern.

07:13.561 --> 07:15.458
I don't need to punch in every day

07:15.482 --> 07:17.501
as long as I do my job.

07:17.641 --> 07:18.898
My only task today

07:18.922 --> 07:20.977
is to contact the Perfect Voice Studio.

07:21.001 --> 07:22.081
The Perfect Voice Studio?

07:22.081 --> 07:23.498
The Perfect Voice Studio?

07:23.522 --> 07:24.537
Unbelievable!

07:24.561 --> 07:26.121
The company I'm working at

07:26.121 --> 07:28.258
developed an app and wants to

07:28.282 --> 07:29.737
promote it.

07:29.761 --> 07:31.338
I told you about it.

07:31.362 --> 07:33.938
I'm making Sheng the music director.

07:33.962 --> 07:37.102
You said
you'd make me the music director,

07:37.162 --> 07:39.701
but nothing
about the Perfect Voice Studio.

07:41.722 --> 07:43.018
It's so good.

07:43.042 --> 07:44.941
Try the meat.

07:46.962 --> 07:47.818
They started out

07:47.842 --> 07:50.378
doing dubbing online.

07:50.402 --> 07:51.737
It was a small circle.

07:51.761 --> 07:54.617
They did it purely because they loved it

07:54.641 --> 07:56.898
and gained fame over the years.

07:56.922 --> 07:58.338
Sheng is my senior.

07:58.362 --> 08:00.417
She's always adored Qiang Qingci.

08:00.441 --> 08:03.342
He wasn't known back then, right?

08:04.362 --> 08:06.018
So how did you know him?

08:06.042 --> 08:08.617
It was a promotional video of a game.

08:08.641 --> 08:12.501
I happened to see it.

08:12.802 --> 08:15.982
That's when I heard his voice.

08:19.761 --> 08:23.742
I kind of fell in love with his voice.

08:28.162 --> 08:29.577
What does he sound like?

08:29.601 --> 08:32.018
His voice is totally my type.

08:32.042 --> 08:33.778
He sounds amazing.

08:33.802 --> 08:36.341
How does he look?

08:36.561 --> 08:38.061
I haven't met him.

08:39.242 --> 08:41.262
No one has.

08:41.441 --> 08:43.542
He never shows up.

08:48.242 --> 08:49.341
Here.

08:49.721 --> 08:51.101
Here.

08:53.802 --> 08:55.422
The meat is amazing.

08:57.361 --> 08:59.177
Mr. Mo is the best.

08:59.201 --> 09:01.902
We always get a treat
the day after the performance.

09:02.002 --> 09:03.018
When has he ever

09:03.042 --> 09:04.081
been stingy to you,

09:04.081 --> 09:05.422
Wang Ke?

09:05.721 --> 09:06.297
Yeah, yeah.

09:06.321 --> 09:07.902
Dig in.

09:10.002 --> 09:10.817
I have work to do.

09:10.841 --> 09:11.697
I'll not drink it.

09:11.721 --> 09:13.057
You don't have work today.

09:13.081 --> 09:14.662
The hospital work again?

09:15.002 --> 09:17.498
My colleague is giving birth.
I'm taking her shift.

09:17.522 --> 09:19.142
So busy.

09:19.522 --> 09:21.817
About the tenth anniversary ceremony.

09:21.841 --> 09:23.302
Have you decided?

09:24.601 --> 09:25.738
Don't count me in.

09:25.762 --> 09:26.981
Too busy.

09:27.361 --> 09:28.981
Every time.

09:29.242 --> 09:30.341
Cheers.

09:35.042 --> 09:37.577
But he rarely attends any events.

09:37.601 --> 09:40.361
There are two other people
in the Perfect Voice Studio.

09:40.361 --> 09:42.817
They are the Top Three in the business.

09:42.841 --> 09:43.577
Qiang Qingci.

09:43.601 --> 09:44.457
Juemei Shayi.

09:44.481 --> 09:45.537
Feng Yasong.

09:45.561 --> 09:46.618
They are quite distinctive

09:46.642 --> 09:48.057
and have many fans.

09:48.081 --> 09:50.618
It'd be amazing if you could invite

09:50.642 --> 09:52.138
all three of them.

09:52.162 --> 09:53.057
Yeah.

09:53.081 --> 09:54.537
I just love

09:54.561 --> 09:56.941
taking challenges.

10:02.238 --> 10:04.642
(Hello, I'm Geng Xiaoxing.
Would you attend the event I mentioned?)

10:04.642 --> 10:06.297
It's a girl?

10:06.321 --> 10:07.941
Your girlfriend?

10:08.162 --> 10:09.057
Nonsense.

10:09.081 --> 10:10.177
Someone

10:10.201 --> 10:12.701
is inviting us to promote their app.

10:13.242 --> 10:14.417
Who do they want?

10:14.441 --> 10:16.262
I'm most probably booked.

10:16.721 --> 10:18.898
Not you.

10:18.922 --> 10:23.382
They want the Top Three dubbing actors
of the Perfect Voice Studio.

10:24.282 --> 10:25.542
Not you.

10:26.441 --> 10:29.542
Alright, Top Three.

10:30.172 --> 10:30.882
(App Fufu, Star Child)

10:30.882 --> 10:32.297
Wait.

10:32.321 --> 10:35.181
They invited you and Feng Yasong.
I kind of get it.

10:35.282 --> 10:37.738
But who can possibly
get him to an event?

10:37.762 --> 10:39.657
Seriously, I've checked the list.

10:39.681 --> 10:41.218
I don't know anyone.

10:41.242 --> 10:42.218
Look.

10:42.242 --> 10:44.738
(Main producers)
Do you know Geng Xiaoxing?

10:44.762 --> 10:45.618
No.

10:45.642 --> 10:47.417
Not the rest, either.

10:47.441 --> 10:49.978
(Music director Shengshengman)
And there's a music director.

10:50.002 --> 10:51.018
Shengshengman.

10:51.042 --> 10:51.937
Do you know her?

10:51.961 --> 10:53.662
No.

10:54.122 --> 10:55.581
Shengshengman.

10:56.242 --> 10:56.898
What's wrong?

10:56.922 --> 10:58.341
You know her?

11:01.681 --> 11:02.902
I remember something.

11:05.522 --> 11:06.417
What?

11:06.441 --> 11:08.061
What do you remember?

11:16.757 --> 11:20.384
(Do you sense something?)

11:23.321 --> 11:24.422
What?

11:24.681 --> 11:27.622
Why are you texting me on WeChat?

11:33.122 --> 11:34.978
Mr. Mo, have some chicken.

11:35.002 --> 11:36.522
It's really tender.

11:36.522 --> 11:38.262
Have some soup.

11:39.922 --> 11:40.978
Where are you going?

11:41.002 --> 11:42.422
To get some dipping.

11:43.961 --> 11:44.697
What?

11:44.721 --> 11:48.422
Think about it.
How can he know someone and we don't?

11:50.122 --> 11:51.218
Accept the invitation.

11:51.242 --> 11:52.457
I want to meet Shengshengman.

11:52.481 --> 11:54.018
For what?

11:54.042 --> 11:54.898
To gossip.

11:54.922 --> 11:56.378
It's tiring to talk to you.

11:56.402 --> 11:57.701
So insensitive.

11:58.042 --> 11:59.981
Show some respect.

12:00.481 --> 12:02.101
I'll get some dipping.

12:14.601 --> 12:17.981
(In this play that lasts for ages, )

12:18.282 --> 12:22.061
(we're both playing our parts.)

12:24.841 --> 12:27.181
(His profile lit up by the lamp)

12:27.402 --> 12:30.821
(has the depressing vibe of a playboy.)

12:31.361 --> 12:32.402
(Eventually, she realized...)

12:32.402 --> 12:33.657
Great dubbing.

12:33.681 --> 12:34.601
It got me absorbed.

12:34.601 --> 12:36.201
(Between the dim light and shadows...)

12:36.201 --> 12:37.802
Mr. Mo, another masterpiece.

12:37.802 --> 12:40.461
(He sits on piles of skeletons)

12:41.721 --> 12:44.081
(to defend the nation.)

12:44.081 --> 12:45.937
That was Qiang Qingci.

12:45.961 --> 12:48.138
Attractive and amazing, right?

12:48.162 --> 12:49.542
Sounds amazing.

12:56.122 --> 12:58.142
The food was so good.

12:58.361 --> 13:00.457
Sheng,
your recommended one is really tasty.

13:00.481 --> 13:02.657
Did Juemei reply?

13:02.681 --> 13:04.622
Let me check.

13:07.402 --> 13:10.978
Not yet. I bet he's not interested
because our app is unknown.

13:11.002 --> 13:12.098
And I stressed

13:12.122 --> 13:14.378
our music director is Shengshengman.

13:14.402 --> 13:16.177
I'm nobody.

13:16.201 --> 13:18.138
They wouldn't know me.

13:18.162 --> 13:19.738
No, you're amazing.

13:19.762 --> 13:20.618
Let's wait.

13:20.642 --> 13:21.817
We may be surprised.

13:21.841 --> 13:22.817
Stay positive.

13:22.841 --> 13:23.738
Yeah.

13:23.762 --> 13:25.457
The car is here. Let's go.

13:25.481 --> 13:27.422
Hurry up.

13:29.282 --> 13:31.902
Shengshengman is a poem name, right?

13:33.882 --> 13:35.861
What? Am I wrong?

13:36.042 --> 13:36.898
No.

13:36.922 --> 13:38.701
It's rudimentary knowledge.

13:39.522 --> 13:41.297
We can't drive. Did you drive here?

13:41.321 --> 13:42.577
No.

13:42.601 --> 13:43.858
So what do we do?

13:43.882 --> 13:44.642
Got your bus cards?

13:44.642 --> 13:45.898
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

13:45.922 --> 13:47.622
Mine is here.

14:13.814 --> 14:16.530
(The Perfect Voice Studio)

14:16.882 --> 14:17.817
Really?

14:17.841 --> 14:20.221
Really, Doudou.

14:20.802 --> 14:23.738
Qiang Qingci has...

14:23.762 --> 14:25.221
Surprising?

14:26.522 --> 14:27.902
What's her name?

14:29.402 --> 14:31.057
Shengshengman.

14:31.081 --> 14:32.457
Shengshengman.

14:32.481 --> 14:33.738
Nice name.

14:33.762 --> 14:35.417
They sound like a couple.

14:35.441 --> 14:37.577
Right? That's what I thought.

14:37.601 --> 14:39.858
But are you sure you got it right?

14:39.882 --> 14:42.057
Mr. Mo barely goes online.

14:42.081 --> 14:44.537
How would he know a music director

14:44.561 --> 14:45.902
from online?

14:46.042 --> 14:46.778
This may

14:46.802 --> 14:48.138
seem weird to you.

14:48.162 --> 14:49.537
But you must trust me.

14:49.561 --> 14:50.498
I'm totally trustworthy.

14:50.522 --> 14:51.258
I must...

14:51.282 --> 14:52.701
Mr. Mo.

14:54.762 --> 14:57.742
Mr. Mo, you owe me
a game dubbing this month.

14:57.922 --> 14:59.138
I know. I remember.

14:59.162 --> 15:00.098
When do you need it?

15:00.122 --> 15:01.898
They want it within the month.

15:01.922 --> 15:03.858
It's only 100 lines or so. Two hours.

15:03.882 --> 15:04.738
When are you free?

15:04.762 --> 15:05.937
I'll book the studio.

15:05.961 --> 15:09.537
Make it 10 PM the night after tomorrow.

15:09.561 --> 15:11.262
Okay, deal.

15:11.402 --> 15:12.701
Rest assured.

15:12.961 --> 15:15.221
- Bye, Mr. Mo.
- Bye.

15:16.402 --> 15:17.782
Really.

15:17.922 --> 15:19.262
Really.

15:20.476 --> 15:21.321
(First People's Hospital)

15:21.321 --> 15:22.961
It's so hard
to make an appointment here.

15:22.961 --> 15:24.902
Yeah, exactly.

15:26.291 --> 15:27.162
(Wangjia Supermarket)

15:27.162 --> 15:28.821
Visit us again.

15:28.969 --> 15:31.162
(Wangjia Supermarket)

15:31.162 --> 15:32.941
- Just one?
- Yeah.

15:33.601 --> 15:34.498
Five yuan.

15:34.522 --> 15:35.378
Via WeChat.

15:35.402 --> 15:36.502
Okay.

15:40.841 --> 15:42.742
- Visit us again.
- Thanks.

15:43.841 --> 15:44.697
Sheng.

15:44.721 --> 15:46.902
Come on, help me.

15:48.681 --> 15:49.817
Can't you do it?

15:49.841 --> 15:51.937
You always need help.

15:51.961 --> 15:53.177
Why are you so lazy?

15:53.201 --> 15:55.937
It's better with a helper.

15:55.961 --> 15:57.181
This one.

15:59.162 --> 16:00.302
This one.

16:02.081 --> 16:04.778
The probiotic drinks are selling well.

16:04.802 --> 16:06.061
Put some more.

16:13.042 --> 16:14.782
You're sneaking one again?

16:14.841 --> 16:16.898
You really think we run this supermarket

16:16.922 --> 16:18.498
for you to have free food?

16:18.522 --> 16:19.618
Did you note it down?

16:19.642 --> 16:21.101
Put it on my bill.

16:21.841 --> 16:22.522
Yeah, yeah.

16:22.522 --> 16:23.657
You want some?

16:23.681 --> 16:24.697
No, thanks.

16:24.721 --> 16:26.581
Go away. Don't mess things up.

16:29.522 --> 16:31.018
Won't you help me?

16:31.042 --> 16:32.461
You're on your own.

16:34.042 --> 16:35.417
(Breaking news.)

16:35.441 --> 16:36.498
(They said yes.)

16:36.522 --> 16:38.701
(The Perfect Voice Studio
will work with us.)

16:38.882 --> 16:40.378
(Breaking News No. 2.)

16:40.402 --> 16:41.782
(Deep breath.)

16:43.321 --> 16:44.282
(Today, at 6 PM, )

16:44.282 --> 16:46.258
(they want an online meeting with us.)

16:46.282 --> 16:49.262
(At 6 PM, the Top Three will be there.)

16:50.321 --> 16:52.341
Gu Jia, what time is it?

16:53.161 --> 16:54.641
5:40 PM. Why?

16:54.641 --> 16:55.321
(5:40 PM)

16:55.321 --> 16:56.482
(Twenty minutes by bike.)

16:56.482 --> 16:58.161
(I won't make it. Ten minutes by car.)

16:58.161 --> 16:59.442
(Turn on the PC in five minutes.)

16:59.442 --> 17:00.218
(I'm out of time.)

17:00.242 --> 17:02.778
Gu Jia, I have things to do.
I'm going home.

17:02.802 --> 17:03.577
Watch the store.

17:03.601 --> 17:05.121
We're not off work. Where are you going?

17:05.121 --> 17:05.938
It's important.

17:05.962 --> 17:07.097
Wait. What's the rush?

17:07.121 --> 17:07.778
It's important.

17:07.802 --> 17:09.297
Bye.

17:09.321 --> 17:11.821
Put on the jacket. It's cold outside.

17:16.482 --> 17:17.821
Thanks, sir.

17:30.081 --> 17:31.297
Hello, Sheng.

17:31.321 --> 17:32.982
- Sister.
- Hello, Auntie.

17:41.802 --> 17:42.978
Father, Grandfather.

17:43.002 --> 17:44.341
Hey, there.

17:45.161 --> 17:46.581
I'll be in my room.

17:50.802 --> 17:53.542
What's the rush?

18:02.242 --> 18:03.942
Headphones.

18:10.869 --> 18:13.106
(Chat and find friends)
(Shengshengman)

18:17.401 --> 18:19.902
(Doudoubing)
Xiaoxing. I saw your project plan.

18:19.902 --> 18:21.462
I like it. It's meaningful.

18:22.401 --> 18:23.542
Thank you, Doudou.

18:24.002 --> 18:27.178
Our next major event will be
the studio's tenth anniversary.

18:27.202 --> 18:28.097
(He's not here yet.)

18:28.121 --> 18:29.938
We will organize a big promotion.

18:29.962 --> 18:33.101
(Geng Xiaoxing, I'm here.)
It's a great chance for cooperation.

18:33.401 --> 18:34.337
Juemei.

18:34.361 --> 18:36.262
That's exactly what I thought.

18:36.802 --> 18:37.482
I remember...

18:37.482 --> 18:38.218
(I'm here.)

18:38.242 --> 18:39.762
We release a musical song

18:39.762 --> 18:41.057
every year.

18:41.081 --> 18:42.857
(Wang Ke)
What about this year, Doudou?

18:42.881 --> 18:45.418
(Shengshengman)
It's the same. But do you have time to record it?

18:45.442 --> 18:46.537
Someone's here.

18:46.561 --> 18:47.821
I'm on standby.

18:54.042 --> 18:55.978
(Qiang Qingci)
So you've been there.

18:56.002 --> 18:58.018
Why didn't you say something?

18:58.042 --> 18:59.498
I've been here.

18:59.522 --> 19:01.377
But I'm not talking to you.

19:01.401 --> 19:02.617
Close the mic.

19:02.641 --> 19:03.702
Alright.

19:04.002 --> 19:06.290
(Qiang Qingci)

19:06.921 --> 19:08.302
Shengshengman.

19:15.841 --> 19:17.381
Yeah.

19:18.081 --> 19:19.462
Shengshengman.

19:20.181 --> 19:21.537
(Qiang Qingci)

19:21.561 --> 19:23.982
(Geng Xiaoxing)
Sheng, he's calling you.

19:24.522 --> 19:25.978
I'm here.

19:26.002 --> 19:27.341
Sheng.

19:27.522 --> 19:28.821
Are you there?

19:28.962 --> 19:30.421
Yeah.

19:32.841 --> 19:34.617
I bet she's eating something.

19:34.641 --> 19:36.462
What a foodie.

19:42.722 --> 19:44.542
I forgot the mic.

19:46.401 --> 19:49.097
(Shengshengman)
Sorry, I forgot the mic.

19:49.121 --> 19:50.421
I'm here.

19:52.962 --> 19:56.302
Have you tried to make
the pork stomach with chicken?

19:57.282 --> 19:59.061
(He remembers.)

20:01.722 --> 20:03.542
Not yet.

20:03.722 --> 20:05.901
I didn't have time.

20:08.277 --> 20:11.026
(Shengshengman)

20:11.722 --> 20:13.537
(Is it impolite?)

20:13.561 --> 20:16.178
(He told me
how to make it step by step.)

20:16.202 --> 20:18.702
(I should at least show interest.)

20:20.321 --> 20:23.577
Thank you for your instruction.

20:23.601 --> 20:28.381
I will try it for sure.

20:33.199 --> 20:35.410
(Your computer needs to be restarted.)

20:37.813 --> 20:39.482
(Qiang Qingci offline)

20:39.482 --> 20:41.377
(Why is he offline?)

20:41.401 --> 20:43.421
(Is he upset?)

20:46.081 --> 20:48.262
On your PC?

20:48.522 --> 20:49.617
Put it away.

20:49.641 --> 20:51.742
Come downstairs.

20:52.401 --> 20:54.297
Sheng, hurry up.

20:54.321 --> 20:56.381
Got it.

21:01.641 --> 21:02.577
Mother.

21:02.601 --> 21:03.861
What's wrong?

21:04.081 --> 21:05.137
Your cousin

21:05.161 --> 21:07.458
said you left the supermarket
without having food.

21:07.482 --> 21:09.341
What's the rush?

21:10.321 --> 21:12.258
I didn't have time. I had to talk

21:12.282 --> 21:13.297
to Geng Xiaoxing.

21:13.321 --> 21:14.097
Alright.

21:14.121 --> 21:15.297
Here's the noodle.

21:15.321 --> 21:16.458
Eat it.

21:16.482 --> 21:17.337
Thank you, mother.

21:17.361 --> 21:19.061
I'll eat upstairs.

21:19.242 --> 21:21.297
Why don't you eat it here?

21:21.321 --> 21:23.262
Slow down.

21:34.581 --> 21:36.434
(1 message from Qiang Qingci)

21:38.290 --> 21:40.242
(1 message from Qiang Qingci)

21:45.601 --> 21:46.658
(I forgot to tell you.)

21:46.682 --> 21:49.522
(That dish is also called
"Reincarnation of the Phoenix".)

21:53.161 --> 21:54.942
(Thanks.)

21:55.321 --> 21:56.057
(You're welcome.)

21:56.081 --> 21:57.218
(Your name reminds me)

21:57.242 --> 21:59.061
(of a nice dish.)

22:03.522 --> 22:04.901
(What is it?)

22:05.121 --> 22:07.421
(Okra stuffed with shrimp paste.)

22:10.482 --> 22:12.462
(Sounds tasty.)

22:13.202 --> 22:14.817
(I tried to make it once.)

22:14.841 --> 22:15.901
(It's easy.)

22:16.401 --> 22:18.782
(Chop the shrimp into a paste.)

22:19.202 --> 22:21.297
(Add scallion and ginger water, )

22:21.321 --> 22:24.097
(cooking wine, salt, MSG, )

22:24.121 --> 22:25.297
(and white pepper.)

22:25.321 --> 22:26.621
(Clean the okra seeds.)

22:26.841 --> 22:29.057
(Fill them up and steam them.)

22:29.081 --> 22:31.061
(Serve with Thai Sweet Chili Sauce.)

22:31.482 --> 22:32.821
(It's really nice.)

22:49.121 --> 22:50.097
Mother.

22:50.121 --> 22:52.498
Do we have any meat,

22:52.522 --> 22:53.938
vegetables, or shrimp left?

22:53.962 --> 22:56.621
Or just make me an egg.

23:00.881 --> 23:02.738
(He's such a foodie?)

23:02.762 --> 23:04.942
(He never mentioned it
in any interviews.)

23:40.282 --> 23:40.938
Mr. Mo.

23:40.962 --> 23:43.061
That's all you have for dinner?

23:45.042 --> 23:47.097
It's so sad. You make lots of money,

23:47.121 --> 23:49.341
but you can't enjoy life.

23:53.202 --> 23:54.617
Don't eat that.

23:54.641 --> 23:56.341
It lacks nutrition.

24:00.321 --> 24:01.458
What's the flavor?

24:01.482 --> 24:02.702
Let me see...

24:07.522 --> 24:09.577
Let me see what you put in there.

24:09.601 --> 24:11.462
I'll make one for myself.

24:15.601 --> 24:16.778
Did you wash your hands?

24:16.802 --> 24:17.861
No.

24:19.641 --> 24:22.141
Doudou,
do you have disposable chopsticks?

24:24.401 --> 24:26.421
- Thanks.
- Want some noodles?

24:26.722 --> 24:27.738
No, thanks.

24:27.762 --> 24:29.097
You can't cook.

24:29.121 --> 24:31.821
Mr. Mo makes better noodles.

24:32.561 --> 24:34.097
Whatever.

24:34.121 --> 24:35.817
He never saves noodles for anyone.

24:35.841 --> 24:36.938
Stop daydreaming.

24:36.962 --> 24:38.258
I'm not anyone.

24:38.282 --> 24:39.982
Of course, he saved me some.

24:45.682 --> 24:46.682
Alright.

24:47.321 --> 24:48.658
I'll get a takeout.

24:48.682 --> 24:49.778
A hot pot.

24:49.802 --> 24:52.537
No, you filled the room
with that smell last time.

24:52.561 --> 24:54.262
Have this.

24:55.921 --> 24:58.861
Fine, it's better than nothing.

25:01.841 --> 25:02.861
Mr. Mo.

25:03.921 --> 25:06.302
I've been dying to ask you something.

25:07.202 --> 25:09.222
How did you meet

25:10.401 --> 25:12.222
Shengshengman?

25:16.002 --> 25:17.182
You're curious?

25:17.962 --> 25:19.097
Very curious.

25:19.121 --> 25:21.502
Tell me all about it.

25:24.401 --> 25:27.302
It was an accident.

25:27.522 --> 25:28.121
Are you done?

25:28.121 --> 25:29.462
Accident. Wait.

25:29.601 --> 25:30.982
That's it?

25:31.202 --> 25:33.097
How did it happen?

25:33.121 --> 25:35.341
Between whom?

25:35.401 --> 25:37.022
So secretive.

25:40.841 --> 25:42.061
Doudou.

25:42.962 --> 25:44.018
- Doudou.
- What?

25:44.042 --> 25:45.621
- One question.
- Go ahead.

25:47.081 --> 25:49.218
When are we holding the meeting

25:49.242 --> 25:50.658
for that app promotion?

25:50.682 --> 25:53.901
Just ask me
when we will meet Shengshengman.

25:55.641 --> 25:56.942
When?

25:57.601 --> 25:58.901
In two weeks.

25:59.802 --> 26:01.577
But it's our tenth anniversary.

26:01.601 --> 26:04.778
I can invite them to some events.

26:04.802 --> 26:06.658
I don't know if they'd come, though.

26:06.682 --> 26:08.861
Of course, they would.

26:09.321 --> 26:10.702
What about him?

26:14.242 --> 26:15.702
I bet

26:15.802 --> 26:17.702
he'd come

26:17.762 --> 26:19.137
for Shengshengman.

26:19.161 --> 26:20.182
Alright.

26:20.282 --> 26:23.762
Let's do a live stream
during the New Year Festival.

26:23.762 --> 26:26.366
(The Perfect Voice Studio Live Stream)

26:26.366 --> 26:26.910
(8 PM, Jan. 1)

26:26.910 --> 26:28.535
(The Perfect Voice Studio Live Stream
Send)

26:28.535 --> 26:30.002
(Perfect Voice Studio Weibo)

26:30.824 --> 26:31.614
(Doudou: See you there.)

26:31.614 --> 26:32.946
(Comments)

26:32.946 --> 26:34.910
(Repost)

26:34.910 --> 26:36.158
(Like)

26:36.158 --> 26:39.230
(Look forward to it!)

26:39.230 --> 26:41.118
(8 PM, Jan 1)

26:41.118 --> 26:43.378
(Top dubbing actors live streaming!)
(See you there.)

26:43.601 --> 26:45.498
(Happy New Year)
Father, Happy New Year.

26:45.522 --> 26:46.698
Happy New Year.

26:46.722 --> 26:47.698
Happy New Year.

26:47.722 --> 26:48.738
Happy New Year.

26:48.762 --> 26:50.081
- Happy New Year.
- Happy New Year.

26:50.081 --> 26:51.010
Come on.

26:51.034 --> 26:52.626
(Juemei and Feng Yasong are here.)

26:53.486 --> 26:54.014
(60,000 fans.)

26:54.014 --> 26:55.698
(46 online. 76 now.)

26:56.422 --> 26:57.278
(Where are you?)

26:57.302 --> 27:00.313
(We're holding a family feast.)

27:00.313 --> 27:02.386
(Qiang Qingci is arriving.
Seize the chance.)

27:22.932 --> 27:25.042
(Current channel: Feng Yasong)

27:25.722 --> 27:27.861
Isn't it a girl's line?

27:28.042 --> 27:29.621
Never mind. It's okay.

27:30.282 --> 27:33.381
Silence presides over the dim-lit night.

27:33.482 --> 27:37.418
I swallow my tears and put up a smile.

27:37.442 --> 27:39.821
Juemei. Can I ask you something?

27:40.612 --> 27:41.242
(Juemei Shayi)

27:41.242 --> 27:42.137
Go ahead.

27:42.161 --> 27:43.577
Can you do female dubbing once?

27:43.601 --> 27:45.178
It's me every time.

27:45.202 --> 27:46.817
I have a guy's voice.

27:46.841 --> 27:49.101
No one would enjoy it.

27:49.482 --> 27:51.178
Where is Mr. Qiang?

27:51.202 --> 27:52.914
(Online)

27:53.962 --> 27:55.341
Next to me.

27:55.921 --> 27:56.978
His computer went down.

27:57.002 --> 27:58.942
We're sharing a mic.

27:59.002 --> 28:01.302
I'm here. Carry on.

28:01.401 --> 28:03.658
So many people
are waiting to hear from you.

28:03.682 --> 28:05.418
I guess you have to

28:05.442 --> 28:07.178
say something.

28:07.202 --> 28:08.658
Sorry, guys.

28:08.682 --> 28:11.297
I'm having a sore throat.

28:11.321 --> 28:12.702
I'm a bit tired.

28:14.119 --> 28:15.646
(Interactions)

28:15.646 --> 28:17.970
(Mr. Qiang, stop talking. Take care.)

28:18.121 --> 28:19.458
Look at the comments.

28:19.482 --> 28:21.542
People are feeling for Mr. Qiang.

28:22.482 --> 28:24.938
Why are you bossing him around?

28:24.962 --> 28:26.418
That's a false accusation.

28:26.442 --> 28:27.458
I didn't say anything.

28:27.482 --> 28:29.821
And they say I'm bossing you around.

28:32.442 --> 28:34.258
What's wrong? Are you tired?

28:34.282 --> 28:35.982
Go home and rest.

28:37.535 --> 28:39.346
(Online Shengshengman)

28:42.786 --> 28:44.658
(Shengshengman)

28:45.962 --> 28:48.621
I rarely have a day off.
I don't want to sleep yet.

28:53.202 --> 28:55.938
I tried a dish today.

28:55.962 --> 28:57.462
It was good.

28:57.921 --> 28:59.702
Another dish?

28:59.778 --> 29:01.161
(Shengshengman)

29:01.161 --> 29:02.742
It's so late.

29:03.361 --> 29:05.182
Let's go for something plain.

29:06.887 --> 29:09.938
(He's making us crave food.)

29:11.202 --> 29:13.617
I'm only available now.

29:13.641 --> 29:16.502
Don't you like food? Then I'll stop.

29:17.081 --> 29:18.178
Don't.

29:18.202 --> 29:20.537
(Go ahead.)
The fans have been waiting.

29:20.561 --> 29:22.462
Go on. We can handle this.

29:22.962 --> 29:24.337
Alright, stop teasing us.

29:24.361 --> 29:26.821
Let's go for
a late-night snack afterward.

29:27.601 --> 29:28.702
Okay.

29:31.321 --> 29:32.821
First.

29:33.282 --> 29:35.222
Let me tell you about

29:35.722 --> 29:37.982
fish-flavored eggplants.

29:38.242 --> 29:39.458
This dish

29:39.482 --> 29:41.702
consists of deep-fried eggplants

29:41.921 --> 29:45.101
and fish-flavored sauce.

29:57.002 --> 29:59.061
Get two eggplants.

29:59.682 --> 30:01.262
Slice them up.

30:17.161 --> 30:18.942
Cut through three-fourths

30:19.121 --> 30:21.182
and keep it attached.

30:21.361 --> 30:23.182
Then chop it off.

30:24.242 --> 30:26.341
It gets better flavor like that.

30:28.081 --> 30:30.302
Roll them in flour mixed with eggs.

30:30.682 --> 30:33.982
Deep-fry until both sides
turn golden and crispy.

30:35.282 --> 30:37.782
Fry the garlic and peppers.

30:38.442 --> 30:40.661
Add the eggplants.

30:41.921 --> 30:43.742
Remember the spices.

30:43.881 --> 30:45.341
Soy sauce.

30:45.641 --> 30:46.661
Pepper.

30:47.002 --> 30:48.061
Sugar.

30:48.121 --> 30:50.222
MSG, and vinegar.

30:51.161 --> 30:52.542
Stir fry on high fire.

30:52.881 --> 30:55.462
Add peanuts and scallions.

30:56.881 --> 30:58.782
And it's ready.

31:24.722 --> 31:25.861
Mother.

31:26.601 --> 31:27.901
What?

31:28.121 --> 31:30.401
Do we have noodles or something like

31:30.401 --> 31:32.218
Liuzhou River Snails rice noodles?

31:32.242 --> 31:34.742
Dinner wasn't enough?

31:36.417 --> 31:38.226
(1 message from Qiang Qingci)

31:38.921 --> 31:40.621
Forget it. I'm good.

31:45.081 --> 31:46.081
(You there?)

31:49.002 --> 31:50.022
(I'm here.)

31:55.081 --> 31:58.421
(It's sour and spicy,
which brings up your appetite.)

32:00.361 --> 32:03.061
(Okay, I'll try it one day.)

32:03.561 --> 32:06.022
(Okay, see you next time.)

32:08.042 --> 32:10.022
Let's go for a night snack.

32:11.321 --> 32:12.502
Night snack?

32:13.361 --> 32:14.661
I'll pass.

32:18.641 --> 32:19.817
I'm heading back

32:19.841 --> 32:21.341
to the hospital.

32:28.921 --> 32:30.901
So fishy.

32:34.002 --> 32:35.377
You're heading out?

32:35.401 --> 32:36.942
Where are you going?

32:37.121 --> 32:39.137
I'm hungry. I'll get skewers.

32:39.161 --> 32:41.097
I thought you weren't hungry anymore.

32:41.121 --> 32:42.817
I'm hungry again.

32:42.841 --> 32:44.738
Pass by the supermarket.

32:44.762 --> 32:47.018
Gu Jia has to close the store
and keep the account.

32:47.042 --> 32:48.658
He could need some help.

32:48.682 --> 32:49.658
Okay, I see.

32:49.682 --> 32:53.057
Sheng, take Peanut out for a walk.

32:53.081 --> 32:53.817
Alright.

32:53.841 --> 32:54.762
See you.

32:54.762 --> 32:56.018
That's your job.

32:56.042 --> 32:57.617
I'm doing accounting.

32:57.641 --> 32:59.222
Don't be late.

33:02.482 --> 33:04.421
Wait.

33:07.682 --> 33:09.061
Peanut.

33:09.282 --> 33:10.377
Where are you going?

33:10.401 --> 33:11.742
Are you hungry?

33:12.962 --> 33:14.002
Slow down.

33:14.002 --> 33:14.938
Doudou.

33:14.962 --> 33:16.617
(Wangjia Supermarket)
Let's go, Peanut.

33:16.641 --> 33:17.778
Let's go to work.

33:17.802 --> 33:19.498
Doggie. So cute.

33:19.522 --> 33:20.170
- Let's go.
- Bye.

33:20.194 --> 33:23.002
(Wangjia Supermarket)

33:23.002 --> 33:25.381
Gu Jia, I brought Peanut.

33:25.522 --> 33:28.022
Peanut, would you like to eat something?

33:28.282 --> 33:30.061
What do you like?

33:31.722 --> 33:32.861
Dr. Mo.

33:33.561 --> 33:34.698
You're off work?

33:34.722 --> 33:36.377
I'm getting something to drink.

33:36.401 --> 33:37.377
I'll come back.

33:37.401 --> 33:40.022
Are you working overtime?

33:40.282 --> 33:42.377
I came back

33:42.401 --> 33:43.738
to check on a patient.

33:43.762 --> 33:45.258
That's impressive.

33:45.282 --> 33:47.561
You're truly our role model.

33:47.561 --> 33:49.978
You make me feel guilty
about going home.

33:50.002 --> 33:51.570
What drink would you like?

33:51.601 --> 33:54.222
Whatever you get. See you around.

33:57.041 --> 33:58.861
Peanut.

34:05.175 --> 34:06.474
(Music player)

34:06.498 --> 34:10.138
♪ We haven't met before that year ♪

34:10.162 --> 34:11.262
Gu Jia.

34:11.722 --> 34:13.658
Why are you playing that?

34:13.682 --> 34:16.262
What a nice song you wrote.

34:16.762 --> 34:18.538
Come on. Turn it off.

34:18.562 --> 34:20.417
It's been years.

34:20.441 --> 34:22.341
You're feeling awkward?

34:23.041 --> 34:24.098
Think about it.

34:24.122 --> 34:27.218
It's like a college kid reading
an article he wrote in secondary school.

34:27.242 --> 34:28.178
It's awkward.

34:28.202 --> 34:29.977
I'm promoting it for you.

34:30.001 --> 34:32.262
Turn it off.

34:33.481 --> 34:35.021
Fine.

34:35.401 --> 34:37.698
Pack up. Let's go for a night snack.

34:37.722 --> 34:39.658
Let me gather the flowers.

34:39.682 --> 34:41.622
Then we can go home.

34:55.162 --> 34:57.381
Sorry, we're closed.

35:01.401 --> 35:03.662
Fine, last customer.

35:13.841 --> 35:15.337
Please hurry up.

35:15.361 --> 35:17.421
We're closing off.

35:25.621 --> 35:31.082
♪ We haven't met before that year ♪

35:32.725 --> 35:38.994
♪ Staring into the starry night ♪

35:39.957 --> 35:46.731
♪ We wonder who we'll
spend our lives with ♪

35:47.381 --> 35:52.850
♪ My thoughts constitute a dream ♪

36:03.669 --> 36:08.882
♪ We just met that year ♪

36:11.282 --> 36:12.821
That's it, right?

36:15.170 --> 36:18.258
(Music player)

36:19.481 --> 36:21.817
It's 27.6 yuan.

36:21.841 --> 36:23.541
Cash or WeChat Pay?

36:27.521 --> 36:28.582
Hello.

36:28.921 --> 36:30.501
Cash or WeChat Pay?

36:34.441 --> 36:35.541
Alright.

36:40.562 --> 36:42.062
Visit us again.

36:53.921 --> 36:54.937
Is there anything else?

36:54.961 --> 36:56.337
We're closing off.

36:56.361 --> 36:58.102
Would you like to get something else?

37:01.202 --> 37:03.062
Visit us again.

37:12.321 --> 37:14.341
Why are you staring at him?

37:15.041 --> 37:16.817
To read his fortune.

37:16.841 --> 37:18.981
You know fortune-telling?

37:19.722 --> 37:21.497
I just started studying it.

37:21.521 --> 37:24.377
His eyes have a unique shape.

37:24.401 --> 37:25.618
Theoretically,

37:25.642 --> 37:27.738
it's a common feature
of persistent people.

37:27.762 --> 37:30.017
They rarely give up on something.

37:30.041 --> 37:33.021
They're highly devoted
to a job or a relationship.

37:34.242 --> 37:36.857
No wonder he always gets

37:36.881 --> 37:38.337
the same thing.

37:38.361 --> 37:39.698
Is he a regular customer?

37:39.722 --> 37:40.618
Yeah.

37:40.642 --> 37:43.501
I think he's a doctor
from across the street.

37:43.961 --> 37:45.582
I'll get the flowers.

37:47.669 --> 37:49.251
(First People's Hospital)

37:49.251 --> 37:52.082
(Emergency, Inpatient)

37:56.122 --> 37:57.137
Dr. Mo.

37:57.161 --> 37:58.381
Give it to me.

37:58.881 --> 38:00.101
Thank you.

38:01.202 --> 38:02.742
Dr. Mo.

38:03.242 --> 38:05.041
Something's wrong with Bed No. 17.
Hurry.

38:05.041 --> 38:06.262
Okay.

38:10.881 --> 38:12.101
Father.

38:13.242 --> 38:14.861
What's going on, Doctor?

38:17.682 --> 38:19.162
It can be a cardiac tamponade.

38:19.182 --> 38:21.498
- Inform the Operating Room of thoracotomy.
- Got it.

38:21.522 --> 38:22.401
Hang in there.

38:22.401 --> 38:23.337
Excuse us.

38:23.361 --> 38:24.377
Excuse us.

38:24.401 --> 38:25.417
Hang in there.

38:25.441 --> 38:26.741
Father.

38:27.541 --> 38:28.222
(Operating Room)

38:28.222 --> 38:29.758
(Under Operation)

38:29.758 --> 38:40.894
(First People's Hospital)

38:52.562 --> 38:53.821
I just made rounds.

38:54.921 --> 38:56.017
- Morning.
- Morning.

38:56.041 --> 38:57.742
- Have you eaten?
- Yeah.

38:58.082 --> 38:59.541
How was the surgery?

39:00.361 --> 39:01.098
It went well.

39:01.122 --> 39:03.782
The patient is quite stabilized now.

39:04.881 --> 39:06.417
I didn't even have

39:06.441 --> 39:08.017
any water last night.

39:08.041 --> 39:09.297
Now I have two more patients.

39:09.321 --> 39:10.698
Help me out.

39:10.722 --> 39:11.977
Alright, no problem.

39:12.001 --> 39:13.341
I'll buy you food.

39:14.602 --> 39:18.861
Right, you were gone for 20 minutes
at the supermarket.

39:19.642 --> 39:20.738
Where were you?

39:20.762 --> 39:22.821
I met an old couple

39:23.481 --> 39:24.778
during my shift.

39:24.802 --> 39:26.297
The grandpa had a cerebral hemorrhage.

39:26.321 --> 39:27.457
His kids were not here,

39:27.481 --> 39:29.857
and he didn't know about the procedures.

39:29.881 --> 39:31.702
So I added him on WeChat.

39:32.001 --> 39:33.098
Last night,

39:33.122 --> 39:35.501
he got temporarily paralyzed.

39:35.642 --> 39:37.337
So,

39:37.361 --> 39:39.062
I went to check on them.

39:39.401 --> 39:40.981
After service?

39:41.521 --> 39:43.297
He came to me first.

39:43.321 --> 39:44.421
It's fate.

39:50.881 --> 39:52.222
You've been

39:52.602 --> 39:54.457
single for too long

39:54.481 --> 39:56.182
and become too gossipy.

39:59.041 --> 40:01.698
You'd better find yourself a girl.

40:01.722 --> 40:03.262
Dr. Zhang Lele.

40:07.481 --> 40:08.738
You're stuffed?

40:08.762 --> 40:10.941
Try this.

40:11.041 --> 40:12.702
It's good for digestion.

40:17.162 --> 40:19.941
Don't call me that again.

40:21.401 --> 40:23.102
You're always single too.

40:25.782 --> 40:27.486
(The Perfect Voice Studio)
You're the first students

40:27.486 --> 40:28.738
in our winter break class.

40:28.762 --> 40:30.497
We expect more to come.

40:30.521 --> 40:32.297
There will be 25 people in total.

40:32.321 --> 40:33.802
Actually, dubbing actors

40:33.802 --> 40:36.122
illustrate stories with voice.

40:36.122 --> 40:37.778
It's a kind of acting.

40:37.802 --> 40:39.921
This is our IT director Mao.

40:39.921 --> 40:41.901
Consult him regarding the equipment.

40:42.722 --> 40:44.481
Some of you wanted to see

40:44.481 --> 40:46.417
the studio and equipment.

40:46.441 --> 40:47.618
Come with me.

40:47.642 --> 40:49.062
Let me show you.

40:49.441 --> 40:50.962
Thanks for your time.

40:52.881 --> 40:54.122
- Mr. Juemei.
- Hello, Mr. Juemei.

40:54.122 --> 40:55.202
I've heard so much about you.

40:55.202 --> 40:55.802
So handsome.

40:55.802 --> 40:56.897
Thank you.

40:56.921 --> 40:58.961
Mr. Juemei,
you have lived up to your title.

40:58.961 --> 40:59.602
Thank you.

40:59.602 --> 41:00.361
So handsome.

41:00.361 --> 41:01.901
Thank you.

41:02.165 --> 41:04.786
(Girl's Dorm)

41:09.562 --> 41:11.622
It's almost bedtime.
Stop fooling around.

41:12.961 --> 41:14.738
Room 6678919.

41:14.762 --> 41:15.401
Password AAAAAA.

41:15.401 --> 41:16.461
Come on in.

41:17.041 --> 41:18.622
Come on in.

41:26.321 --> 41:28.377
(Feng Yasong)
We heard some illustrations.

41:28.401 --> 41:29.981
They lack emotions.

41:30.041 --> 41:31.702
You're not in there.

41:32.162 --> 41:33.457
I'm eavesdropping.

41:33.481 --> 41:35.017
Juemei is showing me

41:35.041 --> 41:38.662
how they train their new people
via QQ voice chat.

41:38.802 --> 41:39.841
I'm out.

41:39.841 --> 41:41.457
I can't spy on their internal training.

41:41.481 --> 41:42.337
Come on.

41:42.361 --> 41:44.102
Let me tell Juemei.

41:46.881 --> 41:47.538
Sheng.

41:47.562 --> 41:49.162
He says it's okay.

41:49.162 --> 41:50.582
Feel free to listen.

41:54.122 --> 41:56.138
When Feng Yasong
first entered the business,

41:56.162 --> 41:59.262
he had no emotions at all.

41:59.321 --> 42:00.538
Come on, Feng Yasong.

42:00.562 --> 42:03.582
Tell us about your gloomy days.

42:03.802 --> 42:05.017
I wasn't illustrative.

42:05.041 --> 42:06.538
I lacked a personal life.

42:06.562 --> 42:07.738
That's an excuse.

42:07.762 --> 42:10.337
What about Qiang Qingci?
He's never been in a relationship.

42:10.361 --> 42:12.578
He was known for dubbing as a playboy.

42:12.602 --> 42:14.381
He's so loyal.

42:14.722 --> 42:17.302
Qiang Qingci never had a girlfriend?

42:17.401 --> 42:18.138
No idea.

42:18.162 --> 42:19.857
Juemei, is he next to you?

42:19.881 --> 42:20.658
Let him show us.

42:20.682 --> 42:21.861
Call him.

42:23.162 --> 42:24.182
Let me try.

42:26.921 --> 42:29.182
Say something.

42:30.082 --> 42:30.602
Come on.

42:30.602 --> 42:31.857
I'm tired today.

42:31.881 --> 42:35.297
Come on, we ran out of topics.

42:35.321 --> 42:36.618
Okay? Please.

42:36.642 --> 42:38.062
I'm tired. Seriously.

42:38.841 --> 42:42.017
Our business partners are there too.

42:42.041 --> 42:44.098
And the music director.

42:44.122 --> 42:45.381
Shengshengman.

42:46.321 --> 42:48.218
Come on, stop hesitating.

42:48.242 --> 42:49.702
Help me out.

42:49.961 --> 42:50.897
Just say something.

42:50.921 --> 42:52.381
Anything.

42:54.069 --> 42:56.210
(Juemei Shayi)

43:00.401 --> 43:01.742
Shengshengman.

43:26.046 --> 43:31.668
♪ We haven't met before that year ♪

43:33.342 --> 43:39.551
♪ Staring into the starry night ♪

43:40.676 --> 43:47.250
♪ We wonder who we'll
spend our lives with ♪

43:47.972 --> 43:53.810
♪ My thoughts constitute a dream ♪

44:04.292 --> 44:09.944
♪ We just met that year ♪

44:11.518 --> 44:17.362
♪ Fate brought us closer ♪

44:18.852 --> 44:25.695
♪ Our paths are meant to cross ♪

44:25.988 --> 44:32.163
♪ In those years of youth and beauty ♪

44:32.996 --> 44:40.041
♪ When we suddenly turned around ♪

44:40.580 --> 44:47.859
♪ Geese were flying back home ♪

44:53.415 --> 44:59.289
♪ The moment I meet you ♪

45:00.414 --> 45:06.970
♪ I know you're the one I want ♪

45:07.901 --> 45:14.610
♪ No need to prove our love in a hurry ♪

45:15.332 --> 45:23.332
♪ Because it will last forever ♪
